quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaf walqur-ani almajeed"
  50,2,"Bal AAajiboo an jaahum munthirunminhum faqala alkafiroona hatha shay-onAAajeeb"
  50,3,"A-itha mitna wakunna turabanthalika rajAAun baAAeed"
  50,4,"Qad AAalimna ma tanqusual-ardu minhum waAAindana kitabun hafeeth"
  50,5,"Bal kaththaboo bilhaqqilamma jaahum fahum fee amrin mareej"
  50,6,"Afalam yanthuroo ila assama-ifawqahum kayfa banaynaha wazayyannahawama laha min furooj"
  50,7,"Wal-arda madadnahawaalqayna feeha rawasiya waanbatnafeeha min kulli zawjin baheej"
  50,8,"Tabsiratan wathikralikulli AAabdin muneeb"
  50,9,"Wanazzalna mina assama-imaan mubarakan faanbatna bihi jannatinwahabba alhaseed"
  50,10,"Wannakhla basiqatinlaha talAAun nadeed"